						<summary>

						<p>Hero-stone set up in a field to the west of the village.</p>						

						<p>Paramēśvara Pallavamalla, circa 9th century.</p>						

						<p>This damaged record registers a gift of 7 <hi rend="italic">kuḻa</hi> of land in memory of a hero who died in a fight with Pallavadhavaḷa in the reign of <hi rend="bold">Paramēśvara Pallavamalla.</hi> </p>						

